   <body>
      <context>
         <p>Follow this procedure to adjust a Gas SSOV limit switch:</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Verify that the burner is switched off on the control panel.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>The burner must be off before starting this procedure. </li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_ogg_xsg_vcc">
                     <image href="media/image1.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_pgg_xsg_vcc"
                            align="center"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Turn the adjusting screw on the limit switch counterclockwise (-) until the Melter HMI touch panel shows that the SSOV is open.</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_g3n_ysg_vcc">
                     <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_h3n_ysg_vcc"
                            align="center"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_ksz_ysg_vcc">
                     <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_lsz_ysg_vcc"
                            align="center"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Turn the adjusting screw clockwise (+) until the Melter HMI touch panel shows the SSOV is closed.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Continue turning the adjusting screw clockwise (+) by one-half of a turn (180
                     degrees). </li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_xbs_1tg_vcc">
                     <image href="media/image4.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            id="image_ybs_1tg_vcc"
                            align="center"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
